00:58:41.355 --> 00:58:52.236
I never knew Lucy; I've seen her on videos before, but she was there, and I've always paid attention to her sister Lynn because she's still here on the earth.

00:58:52.236 --> 00:58:54.392
But she was a twin.

00:59:01.783 --> 00:59:03.015
It's amazing because of what the Lord said: the greater glory would be birthed, and it would be through travail.

00:59:06.402 --> 00:59:11.145
It wasn't just about praying in the spirit and praying in tongues; it's about travail in the spirit.

00:59:21.921 --> 00:59:30.002
And when she used the Scripture and she showed it to me when I was in heaven, I saw it all.

00:59:36.860 --> 00:59:37.203
And I saw Brother Hagin, Kenneth Hagin, and he was walking around.

00:59:37.203 --> 00:59:40.634
Even his mannerism—he's a very quiet man.

00:59:46.124 --> 00:59:53.673
He only spoke very little, but it was amazing because he said, "One of the things I did not say is that you're running out of time.

00:59:53.673 --> 00:59:57.104
The church is running out of time.

00:59:57.104 --> 00:59:58.820
Jesus is coming.

00:59:58.820 --> 01:00:00.774
Do you understand that?

01:00:00.774 --> 01:00:06.281
" Lucy was so adamant about letting me know that we were out of time.

01:00:09.861 --> 01:00:10.137
"You must understand that you're out of time," she said.

01:00:10.137 --> 01:00:13.441
"I've carried this as far as I can.

01:00:13.441 --> 01:00:17.021
Now you have to do this on the earth.

01:00:17.021 --> 01:00:22.162
There must be more prayer on the earth.

01:00:22.162 --> 01:00:25.328
" That's not just casual prayer.

01:00:25.328 --> 01:00:30.756
We have prayer meetings, but we don't pray.

01:00:30.756 --> 01:00:37.088
We have intercessory prayer meetings, and we hardly ever pray.

01:00:38.897 --> 01:00:45.682
The Lord said we must come up to a different level in prayer.

01:00:45.682 --> 01:01:07.245
For if we are assembling ourselves together for intercessory prayer, we must pray like we do on this channel, he said, because there are pieces of what you carry there that I don't carry.

01:01:07.245 --> 01:01:14.100
And when we all come together, we make a whole puzzle.

01:01:14.100 --> 01:01:25.239
There are giftings and abilities inside of you that God's gifted you with that he didn't give me.

01:01:25.339 --> 01:01:36.394
But that's why you may be the finger and I may be the toe, but all of us make a whole body.

01:01:36.394 --> 01:01:41.030
There's not one of us more special than another.

01:01:49.841 --> 01:01:50.127
One might be the elbow, one might be the arm, one might be the rib.

01:01:50.127 --> 01:01:50.984
Who knows?

01:01:50.984 --> 01:01:54.702
All I know is we form a whole body.

01:01:54.702 --> 01:01:58.419
Jesus is the head, but we are the body.

01:01:58.419 --> 01:02:04.995
Jesus turns the body, and we are his if we allow him to be in control.

01:02:04.995 --> 01:02:13.095
But we always like—as I've told you a thousand times—we always stay vertical and we keep humble.

01:02:13.095 --> 01:02:20.223
None of us can do any of this without his grace and by his mercy.

01:02:23.617 --> 01:02:31.763
I don't care how much you think you have a gift; it's all by his grace that you have it in the first place.

01:02:32.781 --> 01:02:35.028
And it's time the church woke up.

01:02:36.125 --> 01:02:42.704
And the Lord showed me, even when Brother Hagin—I'm telling you, it was the way he talked was very stern.

01:02:42.704 --> 01:02:45.171
But he was walking in love.

01:02:45.171 --> 01:02:50.927
But there was such a seriousness in what they both had to say to me.

01:02:55.742 --> 01:02:59.969
It wasn't like we just brought you up here to talk to you because we like you.

01:02:59.969 --> 01:03:04.196
No, this was like battle cries: "We're telling you what's coming.

01:03:10.272 --> 01:03:10.536
You need to wake up.

01:03:10.536 --> 01:03:13.178
You must warn the church.

01:03:28.097 --> 01:03:30.376
You must tell the church.

01:03:32.655 --> 01:03:40.518
" And then Brother Hagin said there were private things that he told me that I will not say on this platform.

01:03:40.518 --> 01:03:43.992
It was about me and my ministry.

01:03:43.992 --> 01:03:53.024
But there are certain things that even I have got to grow in as he prayed for me.

01:03:55.803 --> 01:04:20.302
You know, when you have somebody that you look up to a lot and you've listened to him as a little boy—a young man—all through my teenage years, listening to teaching after teaching, and then have a face-to-face meeting with him in heaven after he's gone and be able to see him talk to me.

01:04:20.302 --> 01:04:24.646
And he knew my name.

01:04:42.1000 --> 01:04:43.468
I went, 'Oh.

01:04:43.468 --> 01:04:58.461
' I don't give man any praise, but there are certain people that have helped me along the way and helped me stay.

01:04:58.461 --> 01:05:16.171
Whenever Megan was first diagnosed with autism and his teachings helped us—Diana and I both—I'm so thankful that God would allow me to talk to him.

01:05:23.348 --> 01:05:33.105
And an impartation happened—that and the fire that hit me—and for prayer and for the things that he told me I was going to do.

01:05:36.503 --> 01:05:52.923
I don't know what the Lord meant by a portal to bring messages back and to say things; I don't know what all that means.

01:05:52.923 --> 01:05:58.019
I'm still praying over it.

01:05:58.019 --> 01:06:25.877
But Brother Hagin said, right before the coming of the Lord, 'For what I have seen, the impartation of what I was never able to reveal was that the revival will take place for two years.

01:06:25.877 --> 01:06:38.354
' And whenever he gave it over, it looked like a kumquat, one of those little fruits.

01:06:44.073 --> 01:06:45.633
And he had it, and it dropped inside of me.

01:06:49.339 --> 01:06:52.305
And he said to me, 'Impart a part of...

01:06:52.305 --> 01:07:05.442
' what I thought was interesting about the revival and what he said about the two years and things that he said.

01:07:10.527 --> 01:07:32.623
When I talked to Sister Billie on the phone today, we talked for over an hour about all this and went over the things that the Lord had shown me because she judges all the words, and if she feels something is off, she always will correct me.

01:07:36.924 --> 01:07:38.879
But as I delivered this, she said, 'I believe that's right.

01:07:38.879 --> 01:07:42.789
' She was real sweet about it.

01:07:42.789 --> 01:07:47.481
She listened because she knew these people personally.

01:07:49.908 --> 01:07:55.322
And she told me a story about another man of God.

01:07:55.322 --> 01:08:14.520
I don't know if I have her permission to talk about it, so I won't, but she talked about some other elders and things that have happened similarly.

01:08:14.520 --> 01:08:17.965
So that's what I'll say.

01:08:17.965 --> 01:08:31.503
But it just gets me excited for where we are, ladies and gentlemen, and how Jesus is coming so soon.

01:08:31.503 --> 01:08:43.794
I want you to be ready; I want you to have an anticipation for what's about to happen.

01:08:43.794 --> 01:09:02.635
When I saw the emerald color of this new fire, what I was trying to describe was what the Lord was showing me about the 12 tribes of Israel.

01:09:02.635 --> 01:09:09.595
Every single one had a stone, and an emerald represented something.

01:09:15.686 --> 01:09:16.121
And he said, 'Sapphires Healing Ministry.

01:09:16.121 --> 01:09:24.268
' And he went on and he told me what each color represented.

01:09:29.352 --> 01:09:29.743
And the red was prophetic; emerald was watchmen.

01:09:29.743 --> 01:09:39.130
There were certain things that were attached to intercessory prayer gifts and what they were attached to.

01:09:41.085 --> 01:09:45.779
The stones—a color represented something: the twelve tribes, the tribes of Israel.

01:09:45.779 --> 01:09:58.039
But he said, 'I have these mantles for the end times with key generals that will walk in the days ahead.

01:09:58.039 --> 01:10:03.432
' And Jesus spoke to me: 'That's the fire.

01:10:03.432 --> 01:10:08.409
' And it was a ball of fire.

01:10:15.462 --> 01:10:20.896
And he spoke to me—and I didn't get into all what he said—but it was the most beautiful, green, beautiful experience.

01:10:20.896 --> 01:10:28.667
As he said, 'This door was opening,' and he said, 'I want you.

01:10:28.667 --> 01:10:36.848
You're going to start to travel in between, and heaven and earth will collide.

01:10:36.848 --> 01:10:45.028
' Now, as of the first of Passover, there'll be an acceleration of things.

01:10:45.028 --> 01:10:54.519
He warned me again: it's time for breakthrough; it's time for an acceleration of things.

01:10:54.519 --> 01:11:05.978
On Passover, which is Wednesday, you will see a doubling of the birthing pains.

01:11:08.672 --> 01:11:20.525
And so we talked about this, and I probably say that the Shemitah cycle goes into 2028 to 2029.

01:11:29.146 --> 01:11:47.203
And I was talking about how we both—and even what she—we talked about it so many times about how the Shemitah cycle—the rapture of the church—will start during the Shemitah cycle of that period of 2028-2029.

01:11:47.203 --> 01:11:58.488
Not that it could be this seven-year cycle, but it could be the next seven-year cycle.

01:11:58.488 --> 01:12:07.810
But it will always be at the end of a seven-year Shemitah cycle.

01:12:17.607 --> 01:12:27.202
And so she was talking about how it's up, and when Brother Hagin said, 'Two years,' could it be 2027-2028 for the great outpouring of what he was talking about?

01:12:30.857 --> 01:12:45.130
And going over things, I just want you to have an expectation that something major is about to happen in this earth, as we see Israel and the escalation of war.

01:12:54.820 --> 01:12:55.143
And the Lord says, 'I am bringing liberation to the people.

01:12:55.143 --> 01:13:01.603
' And a major revival is coming, and great pressure is coming on Canada.

01:13:01.603 --> 01:13:11.106
And you see them pass the bills like the Lord said they would.

01:13:11.106 --> 01:13:28.938
Everything is lining up for a major persecution, for a major beast system coming, for a shaking of finances with the oil—a shaking of finances with these things.

01:13:32.429 --> 01:13:36.697
And we could be right on the edge of a major move of God.

01:13:36.697 --> 01:13:40.189
Are you ready for it tonight?

01:13:40.189 --> 01:13:51.515
Before we go on to the prayer part of this, I have to keep asking you: is your church ready?

01:13:51.515 --> 01:13:55.364
Are you ready?

01:13:55.364 --> 01:14:00.923
Are you looking for the signs of the times?

01:14:00.923 --> 01:14:03.917
Are you looking at them?

01:14:03.917 --> 01:14:06.482
Are you seeing them?

01:14:06.482 --> 01:14:11.614
Do you have your eyes to the skies?

01:14:16.746 --> 01:14:17.173
Is your heart full with oil for him?

01:14:25.205 --> 01:14:25.620
Are you looking for him?

01:14:28.942 --> 01:14:29.358
Are you yearning for him?

01:14:29.358 --> 01:14:34.341
Jesus, I can't do this life without you.

01:14:40.986 --> 01:14:41.401
I just want to encourage you tonight to be all in.

01:14:41.401 --> 01:14:46.988
It's time to come up higher in our prayer time.

01:14:53.000 --> 01:14:55.848
We will not get the job done until it's birthed in the spirit first, and it will come through travail.

01:14:55.848 --> 01:14:58.063
It will come through prayer.

01:14:58.063 --> 01:15:11.825
So ask the Holy Spirit tonight to give you a greater gift of intercessory prayer to pray for the nations, to stir up the gift that you already have.

01:15:11.825 --> 01:15:18.041
But to go deeper with him is what I'm trying to say.

01:15:18.041 --> 01:15:22.794
Not just ankle-deep, not just knee-deep, not just waist-deep.

01:15:22.794 --> 01:15:27.181
Let's go to the bottom of the pool.

01:15:32.828 --> 01:15:33.155
We must come up higher, and you must surrender more to him.

01:15:39.368 --> 01:15:39.695
Jesus, I want to help you.

01:15:39.695 --> 01:15:40.676
Use me.

01:15:40.676 --> 01:15:43.945
Teach me to pray on another level.

01:15:49.831 --> 01:15:50.158
I want to be one of your end-time prayer warriors.

01:16:00.563 --> 01:16:01.474
The Lord told us you'll bring prayer to the nations, and in doing so, there will be a million-man and woman prayer army eventually with you.

01:16:06.338 --> 01:16:09.986
You will pray, and you will change things, and it will bring forth the glorious outpouring as we pray together.

01:16:26.034 --> 01:16:26.508
He said, 'Brandon, I've assembled the greatest prayer warriors of this generation on this channel.

01:16:26.508 --> 01:16:27.931
They're coming.

01:16:45.008 --> 01:16:45.483
I'm commissioning them.

01:16:45.483 --> 01:16:49.752
I'm stirring them up to come.

01:16:49.752 --> 01:16:57.816
' So tonight I have to ask you: Are you all in?

01:16:57.816 --> 01:17:00.951
Are you looking for him?

01:17:00.951 --> 01:17:05.230
Is your heart hungry for the King?

01:17:05.230 --> 01:17:07.798
How desperate, how thirsty?

01:17:07.798 --> 01:17:14.645
How bad is your want-to to go into the deeper rivers?

01:17:14.645 --> 01:17:16.785
He's a gentleman.

01:17:16.785 --> 01:17:21.065
He'll never force his way on you.

01:17:21.065 --> 01:17:31.439
He'll always be the polite one knocking on the door, saying, 'Will you let me in?

01:17:31.439 --> 01:17:34.744
Will you let me in?

01:17:39.939 --> 01:17:40.411
I'm knocking on the door of your heart.

01:17:40.411 --> 01:17:43.716
Will you let me in?

01:17:43.716 --> 01:17:49.855
' It's your job to say, 'Here, my Lord.

01:17:49.855 --> 01:17:51.272
Send me.

01:17:51.272 --> 01:18:01.437
' Like Esther, I've been called to the kingdom for such a time as this.

01:18:01.437 --> 01:18:17.750
As we go into this Holy Week—Passover, Good Friday, Resurrection Sunday—what will the people get when they come to your church?

01:18:17.750 --> 01:18:41.326
We must pray over the protection of our pastors, our churches, and our synagogues—wherever you're going, wherever you're at—for the Jews, for every one of them, for a great protection around and about us.

01:18:41.326 --> 01:18:50.418
Because the Lord showed me major planned attacks like what happened on Palm Sunday in Nigeria.

01:18:50.418 --> 01:18:53.975
All those people are dead now.

01:18:53.975 --> 01:19:00.696
I want to ask you tonight: Do you know my friend Jesus?

01:19:00.696 --> 01:19:03.319
Do you know him?

01:19:03.319 --> 01:19:16.751
And if you're here tonight and you say, 'Brannon, all that sounds so wonderful, but I don't even know Jesus.

01:19:16.751 --> 01:19:24.906
' I don't even know where I would go if I die.

01:19:43.023 --> 01:19:43.522
I want to lead you in a simple little prayer.

01:19:43.522 --> 01:20:00.981
But I want you to be bold before we move on and just tell everybody in the comment section, 'I want to be saved tonight.

01:20:00.981 --> 01:20:05.459
I want to accept Jesus Christ.

01:20:05.459 --> 01:20:10.922
I want to accept him before it's too late.

01:20:10.922 --> 01:20:16.805
' Brother Hagin, they say you're running out of time.

01:20:26.890 --> 01:20:27.310
And even if it was two years, even if it's just a year, I don't know.

01:20:27.310 --> 01:20:43.633
If we're in that time frame right now, in the next two years, whatever, I truly believe that we truly are running out of time on this dispensation of grace.

01:20:52.400 --> 01:20:52.781
But you're here tonight and you feel that tugging on your heart.

01:20:52.781 --> 01:21:02.113
You feel that tugging on your heart and you're saying, 'Brandon, I want to be all in.

01:21:04.064 --> 01:21:07.577
I want to make sure I'm right with the Lord.

01:21:07.577 --> 01:21:23.139
' I want to say a simple prayer for you, and I want you to repeat this prayer after me and believe it and be strong about it.

01:21:23.139 --> 01:21:40.092
Believe it that Jesus Christ loves you and he has a plan for your life, and that you are a sinner and you need a Savior.

01:21:40.092 --> 01:21:53.844
I'm going to say a simple prayer and I want you to say it, and you repeat it after me.

01:22:18.930 --> 01:22:19.412
And when we're done, I want you to be bold about your faith and say, 'Tonight's my night.

01:22:29.064 --> 01:22:29.546
I want to be saved.

01:22:29.546 --> 01:22:35.337
' Let us know if you got saved.

01:22:35.337 --> 01:22:36.785
All right.

01:22:36.785 --> 01:22:43.058
Say: 'Jesus, I believe you're the Son of God.

01:22:51.993 --> 01:22:53.583
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

01:22:53.583 --> 01:23:00.474
Jesus, I'm a sinner and I need a savior.

01:23:00.474 --> 01:23:07.894
As of tonight, I turn my back on my sin.

01:23:16.905 --> 01:23:17.435
I turn my back on the devil.

01:23:22.306 --> 01:23:26.390
I turn my back on any agreements I've made with the devil.

01:23:39.662 --> 01:23:40.173
I break those agreements and I will not serve the devil anymore.

01:23:40.173 --> 01:23:44.767
As of tonight, I am saved.

01:23:44.767 --> 01:23:51.403
I believe that you are the Son of God.

01:24:09.906 --> 01:24:10.329
I believe that tonight my sins are washed in your precious blood.

01:24:10.329 --> 01:24:14.144
Jesus, I surrender all to you.

01:24:21.772 --> 01:24:23.044
I thank you, Lord, that you write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:24:23.044 --> 01:24:33.470
Jesus, I will serve you from this day forward and I give you everything.

01:24:33.470 --> 01:24:37.188
I give you my all.

01:24:37.188 --> 01:24:41.968
Use me, Lord, for your kingdom.

01:24:41.968 --> 01:24:48.341
Let me be a great mouthpiece for you.

01:25:03.975 --> 01:25:04.567
I thank you, Lord, that if I was to die today, I'll be with you in Paradise forever.

01:25:16.406 --> 01:25:16.998
I thank you, Lord, that I am saved.

01:25:16.998 --> 01:25:19.957
Amen and amen.

01:25:19.957 --> 01:26:04.020
' I believe if you just said that simple prayer, as simple as it is, if you believe and confess that Jesus Christ is your personal Savior and that he died and he rose again, and he is the Son of God, I believe you are saved.

01:26:04.020 --> 01:26:08.960
Now, what do you do?

01:26:08.960 --> 01:26:35.173
I would go to a Bible-believing church, one that teaches the Word of God that will get you stirred up from within and teach you the way to go.

01:26:35.173 --> 01:26:53.869
Don't go back to the friend you used to hang around with and say, 'Listen, let's go back to the clubs.

01:26:53.869 --> 01:27:04.828
' Now you need to be separate unto Him and go to church.

01:27:04.828 --> 01:27:14.272
Find a Bible-believing church; a non-denominational church is where we would go.

01:27:14.272 --> 01:27:21.494
Go to the church and get plugged in there.

01:27:21.494 --> 01:27:28.161
Read your Bible every single day and pray.

01:27:28.161 --> 01:27:44.659
Tell the pastor at that church—if it is next week, maybe you go to church for the first time on Easter—say, 'Listen, I want to be water baptized.

01:27:44.659 --> 01:27:56.923
' Get water baptized, get plugged into that church, read your Bible, pray, and come over here and pray with us.

01:27:56.923 --> 01:28:18.695
If you can't afford a Bible and you just said the Sinner's Prayer and gave your heart to Jesus Christ, and you say, 'I don't have a Bible,' my wife and I will send you a Bible for free, no questions asked.

01:28:18.695 --> 01:28:26.879
Just look in the description down below; there is an email down there.

01:28:26.879 --> 01:28:29.894
Say, 'I got saved tonight.

01:28:29.894 --> 01:28:32.478
I want a Bible.

01:28:32.478 --> 01:28:36.355
Can you send me a Bible?

01:28:36.355 --> 01:28:50.396
' Put it in the subject line so we can watch out for it, and we will send you the Bible.

01:28:50.396 --> 01:29:08.189
We just want to celebrate your decision tonight to give your heart to Jesus Christ, and we want to say welcome to the family.

01:29:08.189 --> 01:29:19.179
Get plugged in at your local church and tell your friends that you got saved.

01:29:39.219 --> 01:29:39.703
Say, 'Listen, come with me to church on Sunday.

01:29:39.703 --> 01:29:42.123
It's Easter Sunday.

01:29:42.123 --> 01:29:47.933
Let's go celebrate the resurrection of our Lord.

01:29:47.933 --> 01:29:53.060
' Invite them to come to church.

01:30:13.249 --> 01:30:13.826
It is the largest, busiest Sunday of all Sundays.

01:30:33.077 --> 01:30:33.669
So, I want to tell you all: be encouraged and go to church.

01:30:33.669 --> 01:30:40.775
We always watch Charlton Heston's 'The Ten Commandments.

01:30:40.775 --> 01:30:52.024
' We will be having prayer with you all on Easter and everything.

01:30:52.024 --> 01:31:07.231
Thirty-seven people gave their hearts to Jesus Christ tonight, according to what the numbers show right now.

01:31:07.231 --> 01:31:16.222
To all thirty-seven of you: welcome to the family.

01:31:16.222 --> 01:31:29.559
I'm excited you came tonight and gave your heart to Jesus Christ.

01:31:29.559 --> 01:31:39.473
All thirty-seven of you, welcome to the family.

01:31:39.473 --> 01:31:41.951
That's exciting.

01:32:12.224 --> 01:32:12.753
And so we will go now.

01:32:24.931 --> 01:32:25.460
I don't know, what is this here?

01:32:25.460 --> 01:32:33.932
Okay, this is the video, the one the Lord gave us.

01:32:33.932 --> 01:32:39.227
We got this word—what word was that?

01:32:39.227 --> 01:32:46.110
Yeah, I think this is one of the times.

01:32:48.140 --> 01:32:51.009
I don't know, but, baby, what month?

01:32:51.009 --> 01:32:53.400
September 23rd, 2025?

01:32:53.400 --> 01:32:56.269
Okay, September 23rd, 2025.

01:32:56.269 --> 01:33:02.484
This is what the Lord showed us about Canada.

01:33:08.222 --> 01:33:10.612
The Lord allowed me to see pressure and persecution for His namesake.

01:33:13.003 --> 01:33:13.481
I saw Canada.

01:33:13.959 --> 01:33:22.417
I saw the freedom to be able to say what you want to say.

01:33:22.417 --> 01:33:38.394
Even in our country, the First Amendment—the right to freedom of speech—is being challenged in the days ahead on social media platforms, but mainly in this vision.

01:33:38.394 --> 01:33:47.512
I saw it being challenged in Australia and in Canada, and I saw an olive press.

01:33:47.512 --> 01:33:55.159
As the olive press was pressing the olives, I saw it being tightened and tightened.

01:33:55.159 --> 01:34:03.899
As the olive press was pressing down upon the olives, it was springing forth beautiful olive oil.

01:34:05.720 --> 01:34:14.739
This was a representation, I believe, of a new outpouring and a new press: the pressure on the church.

01:34:14.739 --> 01:34:26.296
Out of the pressure of persecution came beautiful fresh olive oil.

01:34:31.317 --> 01:34:31.875
I saw great darkness.

01:34:31.875 --> 01:35:27.935
I saw a great trial for some, testing your faith, being persecuted for your faith in a way that this generation, a lot of Western society, would not be familiar with compared to what maybe the Far East has experienced: great persecution from China, from the Iron Curtain in North Korea, and the darkness that tries to suppress Christianity all around the world from Iranian Christians who are tortured and murdered without any kind of sympathy at all.

01:35:27.935 --> 01:35:55.261
I saw that a lot of people think they're persecuted in a comment section, which I have been in the past—I don't even read them anymore—but through these keyboard warriors, the Lord says that's not true persecution compared to what a lot of people face.

01:35:55.261 --> 01:36:12.947
When you're dragged down the street by a motorcycle, driving you down the street at 35 or 40 miles an hour and you're being dragged to death, that's great persecution.

01:36:12.947 --> 01:36:18.922
Or losing your head for what you believe; that's persecution.

01:36:18.922 --> 01:36:20.257
That's martyrdom.

01:36:20.257 --> 01:36:30.939
That's what the Lord was showing me: that the Western culture doesn't understand that kind of persecution.

01:36:30.939 --> 01:36:46.865
But as your freedom of speech and other areas are tested in the days ahead, I saw great pressure coming from Canada upon the citizens.

01:36:59.429 --> 01:37:00.199
I saw an olive press pressing, and I saw the church going through a metamorphosis of growth spiritually.

01:37:05.586 --> 01:37:26.790
As you take for granted the very freedoms that you have on a day-to-day basis, when that freedom is challenged and you are called to stand for something and make a choice versus being a coward and hiding, either you stand for something or you lose it.

01:37:26.790 --> 01:37:37.050
Either you get a backbone like a crowbar, or you lose it.

01:37:45.499 --> 01:38:01.150
And the Lord showed me persecution coming upon the church in Europe—persecution coming to the churches because of people being lukewarm and not standing for what they believe.

01:38:13.028 --> 01:38:13.653
You will not be able to take for granted what you truly believe.

01:38:13.653 --> 01:38:17.404
Pastors are great influencers.

01:38:17.404 --> 01:38:32.296
It was sad what I was saying, but I saw a Holy Ghost church rise up out of their slumber.

01:38:39.130 --> 01:38:39.532
I saw a church rise up and say, 'Enough's enough.

01:38:39.532 --> 01:38:47.169
' They stood for what they believed in and they weren't cowards anymore.

01:38:47.169 --> 01:38:51.189
It's kind of like Tommy Hicks's vision.

01:38:51.189 --> 01:39:07.889
If you go back to Tommy Hicks's vision and read about the glorious church, a giant in the land rises up because the Lord points his hand at him.

01:39:10.346 --> 01:39:21.809
The giant rises up and the body comes together and starts moving as one body instead of a bunch of rogue people like Rambos.

01:39:35.142 --> 01:39:35.561
The body comes together.

01:39:35.561 --> 01:40:00.478
And I told you what the Lord said to me: that you will see in the days ahead the body of Christ move as a body and will no longer be: 'Well, you're Baptist, I'm Methodist, I'm Church of Christ, I'm Catholic.

01:40:00.478 --> 01:40:22.843
' No, it was a body joining together with one purpose and one cause, and that's to tell everybody that Jesus Christ is coming and it's time to repent and turn from your wicked ways.

01:40:22.843 --> 01:40:26.951
I saw a glorious church rising.

01:40:26.951 --> 01:40:36.159
I saw a great revival coming from sea to shining sea all around this world.

01:40:36.159 --> 01:40:44.812
We're about to see the greatest harvest of souls this world has ever seen before.

01:40:48.108 --> 01:41:00.120
And we're going to see an outpouring of the Spirit of God like we've never seen before, and great manifestations and demonstrations of the glory.

01:41:11.197 --> 01:41:11.577
But it will come when the church—I saw a great shaking is what I'm trying to tell you.

01:41:22.573 --> 01:41:22.952
I saw a great shaking to awaken, and the church starts to wake, and the giant takes form.

01:41:28.975 --> 01:41:29.437
And there's Brush Arbor churches.

01:41:29.437 --> 01:41:34.985
I saw the old tent revivals coming back.

01:41:34.985 --> 01:41:47.929
I saw, like Mario Cirillo—you know, he does these tent meetings—I saw tent meetings coming back and Holy Ghost meetings.

01:41:47.929 --> 01:41:54.717
I'm trying to tell you what I saw coming again.

01:41:54.717 --> 01:42:13.017
It was dark, but out of the darkness sprung forth great light because the church was no longer lukewarm.

01:42:13.017 --> 01:42:24.539
They realized they were about to be persecuted, even on social media.

01:42:47.863 --> 01:42:48.380
They weren't allowed to say certain things or they would be thrown in jail or persecuted with fines.

01:43:06.936 --> 01:43:07.396
And so the Canadian House of Commons has voted in favor of a bill that makes it possible to convict citizens for certain Bible verses as hate speech.

01:43:07.396 --> 01:43:13.374
And the Lord said it won't rest just there.

01:43:13.374 --> 01:43:18.893
They'll come after your 501(c)(3) status for tax-exempt.

01:43:18.893 --> 01:43:24.516
He said they're going to take that away.

01:43:24.516 --> 01:43:29.210
He said the same thing about America.

01:43:29.210 --> 01:43:35.781
He said they're going to try to take it away.

01:43:35.781 --> 01:43:40.474
They're going to try to persecute Europe.

01:43:40.474 --> 01:43:52.852
But he said what happens in Canada and Europe first, then it will try to come to America eventually.

01:43:52.852 --> 01:43:57.900
I said it will be over social media and all this.

01:43:57.900 --> 01:44:00.739
Watch what happens in the end.

01:44:00.739 --> 01:44:03.578
And that was back in September.

01:44:20.426 --> 01:44:21.034
And here we are.

01:44:21.034 --> 01:44:32.584
March, the Lord said watch Carney, watch this guy as he's a devil.

01:44:41.869 --> 01:44:42.573
So Father, we just thank you for the body.

01:44:42.573 --> 01:44:52.433
Thank you, Father, that we're persecuted for your word's sake.

01:44:58.872 --> 01:45:06.174
But not only that, we rise up in these last days and we're not afraid of man.

01:45:06.174 --> 01:45:09.581
We fear you, not man.

01:45:09.581 --> 01:45:13.962
We humble ourselves before you, Father.

01:45:18.830 --> 01:45:27.105
And we're so thankful, Father, that you have called us to the kingdom for such a time as this.

01:45:49.100 --> 01:45:49.614
And we take this body, God.

01:45:59.202 --> 01:45:59.606
And we remember what you did for us.

01:45:59.606 --> 01:46:12.542
And as we get ready to go into Resurrection week, this beautiful week of Resurrection Sunday, thank you, Jesus, for dying for us.

01:46:12.542 --> 01:46:17.392
Thank you, Jesus, that you didn't just die.

01:46:17.392 --> 01:46:38.304
You whipped the devil once and for all, displaying, making a show of him openly, triumphing over him in it, showing him that he is a loser once and for all.

01:46:57.925 --> 01:46:58.379
And he is defeated.

01:46:58.379 --> 01:47:13.510
And I'm so thankful, Father, that we are seated with you in the heavenlies and we are far above all principalities, just like Ephesians says.

01:47:13.510 --> 01:47:17.131
We're so grateful, Father, for Ephesians.

01:47:17.131 --> 01:47:20.752
It is beautiful; all of it.

01:47:20.752 --> 01:47:24.373
I think the whole thing's amazing.

01:47:24.373 --> 01:47:26.787
I love it all.

01:47:29.604 --> 01:47:37.428
To read Ephesians over and over again, and to take your authority and to be seated as he is.

01:47:37.428 --> 01:47:40.590
So are we in this world.

01:47:42.698 --> 01:47:44.805
And, Father, we thank you for your body.

01:47:44.805 --> 01:47:50.777
You were wounded for our transgressions, you were bruised for our iniquities.

01:47:52.885 --> 01:47:54.993
The chastisement of our peace was upon you.

01:47:54.993 --> 01:47:58.505
And with your stripes, Lord, we're healed.

01:48:04.954 --> 01:48:06.670
And today is the day of the expiration date of what we are believing for.

01:48:06.670 --> 01:48:18.677
And we take this body in the name of Jesus, and we give you glory, honor, and praise for it.

01:48:18.677 --> 01:48:23.986
Lord, we thank you for the blood.

01:48:25.591 --> 01:48:37.894
We make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us in the name of Jesus.

01:48:47.522 --> 01:48:48.057
It never loses its power.

01:49:09.023 --> 01:49:09.421
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that we cover ourselves from the top of our heads to the soles of our feet.

01:49:12.206 --> 01:49:14.593
In the name of Jesus, the blood covers us.

01:49:23.575 --> 01:49:23.984
And I say, I'm yielded to the anointing of the prophetic.

01:49:23.984 --> 01:49:29.705
I yield to the anointing of a watcher and Father.

01:49:29.705 --> 01:49:32.156
I thank you, Lord.

01:49:32.156 --> 01:49:39.920
If there's anything you want to show us tonight, Father, you show us.

01:49:39.920 --> 01:49:44.006
If not, we're not here to perform.

01:49:47.212 --> 01:49:51.204
We attract to deflect, and we always give you the glory.

01:49:51.648 --> 01:50:09.068
And if there's nothing to say tonight, Father, because we've already said it, then, Father, I thank you, Lord, for this time of prayer and fellowship as we go into this week.

01:50:16.191 --> 01:50:19.190
And we praise you, Father, in advance for the blood that covers us in Jesus' name, Amen and Amen.

01:50:19.190 --> 01:50:20.314
All right.

01:50:20.314 --> 01:50:25.343
Whenever I was praying right then, He spoke to me.

01:50:25.343 --> 01:50:28.832
He said, 'Pray over the churches, Brandon.

01:50:30.227 --> 01:50:30.925
Pray over the churches.

01:50:34.762 --> 01:50:35.111
Pray over Easter like I've told you.

01:50:35.111 --> 01:50:38.600
' Sorry to cough in the mic.

01:50:38.600 --> 01:50:42.088
I see myself on the other side.

01:50:42.088 --> 01:50:44.530
I receive it by faith.

01:50:44.530 --> 01:50:45.577
Do we call it in?

01:50:57.989 --> 01:50:58.466
We call in the revival.

01:51:02.755 --> 01:51:03.231
We call in the Holy Ghost waterfall.

01:51:11.810 --> 01:51:13.240
We thank you, Lord, that those old wells of revival are stirring up right now.

01:51:35.772 --> 01:51:36.614
We call the old wells of revival uncapped.

01:51:36.614 --> 01:51:38.297
Uncapped.

01:51:48.397 --> 01:51:49.239
The uncapping of the revival.

01:51:49.239 --> 01:51:50.922
Amen.

01:52:08.665 --> 01:52:09.136
We went to Iran.

01:52:17.605 --> 01:52:18.075
This is a very pivotal week concerning Iran.

01:52:18.075 --> 01:52:32.190
I am praying all up and down the strait right now; I am praying over the water's edge of the strait.

01:52:56.717 --> 01:52:57.313
I see stationed military bases that are all over the Middle East—strategic military bases.

01:53:08.139 --> 01:53:08.496
We pray over the Abraham Lincoln.

01:53:08.496 --> 01:53:12.782
There are so many pictures flashing before me.

01:53:12.782 --> 01:53:20.996
I see Middle Eastern churches; I see mighty worship coming concerning great persecution coming to churches.

01:53:20.996 --> 01:53:24.568
But I see a flame of fire.

01:53:38.813 --> 01:53:39.627
It is on the altar and it is on the pulpit.

01:54:10.466 --> 01:54:10.852
I see a flame of fire.

01:54:10.852 --> 01:54:17.018
Acts Chapter 2 church is coming forth in a greater work.

01:54:17.018 --> 01:54:19.716
Greater works will you do.

01:54:34.183 --> 01:54:37.828
I see it springing forth where great persecution comes; I see a greater level of the glory coming on the church in the Middle East, the underground church in Iran and Iraq.

01:54:37.828 --> 01:54:43.750
Had to get built up by day and time.

01:54:48.761 --> 01:54:49.216
And now I got a daughter and.

01:54:49.216 --> 01:54:52.405
Double trouble for the day.

01:54:52.405 --> 01:54:56.505
Protesters; Justice Thursday brought that today.

01:54:56.505 --> 01:55:02.410
I am seeing North Korea rise up, mocking us.

01:55:02.410 --> 01:55:05.040
You are loosing it.

01:55:05.040 --> 01:55:07.670
You are loosening it.

01:55:07.670 --> 01:55:12.054
We call you to loose it now.

01:55:12.054 --> 01:55:17.752
In Jesus' name, we loosen it and release it.

01:55:21.259 --> 01:55:27.834
It is a dragon that is upon North Korea, and it is going to come down.

01:55:38.321 --> 01:55:38.846
I see a communist dragon that is on it.

01:55:38.846 --> 01:55:48.829
It looks like a red dragon with black teeth, a real crimson red.

01:55:48.829 --> 01:55:55.658
Come on, it's a stronghold, but it's coming down.

01:55:55.658 --> 01:56:01.963
We call on the angels of the Lord.

01:56:01.963 --> 01:56:07.545
Angels of the Lord, bring aid and assistance.

01:56:07.545 --> 01:56:08.881
Remove him.

01:56:08.881 --> 01:56:12.887
We call judgment on the mountain.

01:56:12.887 --> 01:56:16.004
Move out of the way!

01:56:16.004 --> 01:56:16.894
Go!

01:56:39.308 --> 01:56:39.785
The church will rise!

01:56:40.738 --> 01:56:43.121
We call in the revival.

01:56:46.934 --> 01:56:47.411
We call for a shaking.

01:56:49.317 --> 01:56:53.130
We pray for an opening over North Korea.

01:57:03.206 --> 01:57:04.006
We call for an opening, a door, a key.

01:57:04.006 --> 01:57:07.615
More to come.

01:57:07.615 --> 01:57:09.330
Be strong.

01:57:09.330 --> 01:57:12.759
Lose sight of yourself.

01:57:12.759 --> 01:57:23.617
Lose sight of what others think around you as you are leading prayer.

01:57:23.617 --> 01:57:28.761
Lose sight of yourself, prayer warriors.

01:57:28.761 --> 01:57:48.572
You who are in charge of leading prayer, lose sight of yourself and performance, for many of my leaders are there for performance.

01:57:48.572 --> 01:57:53.706
Strip yourself of the pride.

01:57:53.706 --> 01:58:04.159
Come before me by my side, for I am cleansing my bride.

01:58:06.442 --> 01:58:09.296
It is a place of humility.

01:58:20.711 --> 01:58:21.282
It is a place of refining.

01:58:21.282 --> 01:58:26.990
For much humility, strip yourself of pride.

01:58:26.990 --> 01:58:39.864
To know God and to calm the ache as they wait for the greater glory.

01:58:39.864 --> 01:58:47.897
For these sufferings bring forth the greater glory.

01:58:47.897 --> 01:58:49.906
Romans 8:18.

01:58:49.906 --> 01:59:13.337
For I reckon that the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us.

01:59:13.337 --> 01:59:22.197
He's talking about it, and it's echoing through me right now.

01:59:22.197 --> 01:59:34.756
He said, 'For I reckon that the sufferings,' or what's coming: the persecution on the church.

01:59:35.302 --> 01:59:57.606
I see oppression coming in a greater measure, for the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us.

01:59:57.606 --> 02:00:02.606
For it's a cultivation for an acceleration.

02:00:05.606 --> 02:00:16.606
And that's what many of you are about to say: 'This is an Ichabod,' but it is not an Ichabod.

02:00:16.606 --> 02:00:22.606
He is bringing the bride to his side.

02:00:22.606 --> 02:00:33.017
And there is so much haughtiness, and there is humility that must be displayed.

02:00:33.017 --> 02:00:49.045
We have this treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of him and not of us.

02:00:49.045 --> 02:00:55.456
He will not share his glory with anyone.

02:00:59.731 --> 02:01:10.837
The moment you start taking the glory, he said, 'Brandon, how many times have I warned you of what I've even said concerning this?

02:01:10.837 --> 02:01:16.024
I'll not share the glory with you.

02:01:16.024 --> 02:01:16.765
Never.

02:01:16.765 --> 02:01:20.100
Don't touch what belongs to me.

02:01:35.461 --> 02:01:36.046
You know my trigger.

02:01:36.631 --> 02:01:41.310
You want to know my trigger?

02:01:41.310 --> 02:01:47.160
' He said, 'Touch not the glory.

02:01:47.160 --> 02:01:52.451
I'll share it with no one.

02:01:52.451 --> 02:01:57.567
' He said everyone has a trigger.

02:01:57.567 --> 02:02:07.799
Everyone has that thing that will set them off and get them upset inside.

02:02:07.799 --> 02:02:10.868
Touch not the glory.

02:02:10.868 --> 02:02:17.519
Humble yourself before the mighty hand of the Lord.

02:02:18.543 --> 02:02:26.217
But I tell you what I see and what I am hearing.

02:02:26.217 --> 02:02:32.868
I'm traveling over it and I see it inside.

02:02:32.868 --> 02:02:51.982
He said, 'Romans 8:18, for I reckon that the sufferings of this present time are not worthy to be compared with the glory which shall be revealed in us.

02:02:51.982 --> 02:02:57.877
' So you think, what's going on in Canada?

02:02:57.877 --> 02:03:00.598
It's for the present.

02:03:00.598 --> 02:03:06.492
It's not worthy to compare for the glory of what you're about to see.

02:03:06.492 --> 02:03:32.867
And the people, the persecution in North Korea for the glory, and the underground church in Iran, and the underground church in China, and the underground church in North Korea.

02:03:32.867 --> 02:03:39.314
I'm telling you, for the greater glory.

02:03:39.314 --> 02:03:43.181
, so they are correct.

02:03:43.181 --> 02:03:49.628
He said, 'I will not share it.

02:03:49.628 --> 02:04:10.201
' We have this treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of him and not of us.

02:04:30.084 --> 02:04:30.746
It's not about us.

02:04:30.746 --> 02:04:52.190
If you want to be used on a greater level, if you want to speak to greater crowds, you want to do this always.

02:04:52.190 --> 02:04:55.949
Give Him His glory.

02:05:22.478 --> 02:05:23.124
You didn't heal no one.

02:05:23.124 --> 02:05:26.996
Jesus is the healer.

02:05:26.996 --> 02:05:33.450
He could use any one of us.

02:05:48.294 --> 02:05:52.812
The moment you start saying, 'I healed somebody,' and 'Look at me,' you need to realize you're in the wrong lane.

02:05:52.812 --> 02:05:56.576
Jesus is the healer.

02:05:56.576 --> 02:06:10.668
We have a treasure in earthen vessels that the excellency of the power is known of Him and not of us.

02:06:31.358 --> 02:06:32.302
And the Lord said, 'Don't touch the glory.

02:06:32.302 --> 02:06:37.964
Don't take it.

02:06:37.964 --> 02:06:55.470
' Just like, 'Silver and gold have I none; such as I have give I thee.

02:06:55.470 --> 02:07:05.539
In the name of Jesus Christ, rise up and walk.

02:07:05.539 --> 02:07:28.553
' For our light afflictions, which are but for a moment, work for us a far more exceeding and eternal weight of glory.

02:07:28.553 --> 02:07:31.299
Second Corinthians 4:17.

02:07:31.747 --> 02:07:34.436
I like that one better.

02:07:34.436 --> 02:07:48.328
'For our light afflictions, which are but for a moment, worketh for us a far more exceeding and eternal weight of glory.

02:07:48.328 --> 02:07:51.465
' It's the refiner's fire.

02:08:07.839 --> 02:08:08.445
It's the rite of passage.

02:08:08.445 --> 02:08:11.478
Do you understand?

02:08:11.478 --> 02:08:17.542
He said, 'Brandon, share in My glory.

02:08:17.542 --> 02:08:23.000
' He said, 'I will not.

02:08:23.000 --> 02:08:32.704
' It's about stripping yourself down and making yourself that vessel.

02:08:32.704 --> 02:08:36.949
I've been through the fire.

02:08:36.949 --> 02:08:53.544
He said, 'Brandon, I don't allow anybody to go to the greater glory and touch that part of it until they've been refined.

02:08:53.544 --> 02:08:58.791
' Turn it back to that one, honey.

02:08:58.791 --> 02:09:06.226
First Corinthians, I want to read that again: 'For our light affliction...

02:09:06.226 --> 02:09:17.582
' It's the refining; it's the hot, 'Oh, I don't know if I'm going to make it' life's challenges.

02:09:17.582 --> 02:09:28.698
'For our light affliction, which is but for a moment, worketh for us a far more exceeding and eternal weight of glory.

02:09:28.698 --> 02:09:31.208
' It's for our benefit—persecution.

02:09:32.283 --> 02:09:38.021
And I'm talking about the greater glory, travail, bringing it forth through prayer.

02:09:38.021 --> 02:09:42.366
But through travail for the weight of glory.

02:09:44.561 --> 02:09:46.023
It's by the refining fire, He said.

02:09:46.023 --> 02:09:48.583
'It's the rite of passage.

02:09:48.583 --> 02:09:58.823
' Everyone, if you get anywhere in ministry, it's what He told me even yesterday when I had this visitation.

02:09:58.823 --> 02:10:03.943
There's certain things I'm just not going to talk about.

02:10:03.943 --> 02:10:21.151
But He said, 'I'll say this: for our light affliction, which is but for a moment, worketh for us a far more exceeding and eternal weight of glory.

02:10:21.151 --> 02:10:26.980
' He will not share His glory with anyone.

02:10:47.948 --> 02:10:48.475
And if you want to be used in these last days, you strip yourself of pride and always keep yourself small in your own eyes.

02:10:48.475 --> 02:10:52.168
Never forget being a janitor.

02:10:52.168 --> 02:10:56.915
That's what he said to me.

02:10:56.915 --> 02:11:15.073
Never forget it: if you want to be used, if you want to remain, you can be used and have one moment of it.

02:11:15.073 --> 02:11:27.920
But it's more than just something you say; it's something that your heart displays before him.

02:11:27.920 --> 02:11:33.506
What does your heart say before him?

02:11:43.559 --> 02:11:44.118
I can say you can operate a lot of things.

02:11:44.118 --> 02:11:48.028
Well, it sounds really good.

02:11:48.028 --> 02:11:56.683
What Kathryn Kuhlman said: you can parrot a lot of things.

02:12:11.833 --> 02:12:12.322
But what does your heart say before him?

02:12:12.322 --> 02:12:25.517
